        "tree_id": "f4dd32d4ee5a362a3ab3cb5da0fb2e9a50c5a198",
        "message": "build: bundle web/ assets in PyInstaller, bump to 1.1.0\n\nPyInstaller --onefile extracts to sys._MEIPASS at runtime, so the web\nUI directory must be added with --add-data and the loader must\nresolve _MEIPASS first. Also adds explicit hidden imports for the Qt\nWebEngine modules that PyInstaller's static analysis misses.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
