        "message": "feat: initial MacroPad Configurator — PyQt5 desktop app for ESP32-C3 macropad\n\n- Modular module management (add, reorder, sync from device)\n- Button/encoder action assignment (shortcut, media, app, macro, profile switch)\n- OLED preview widget (clock, profile name, volume, custom text)\n- Multi-profile support with JSON persistence in %APPDATA%\\MacroPad\\\n- USB serial communication with ESP32 via JSON protocol (QThread)\n- GitHub Releases auto-update with .bat self-replace on Windows\n- Firmware flash via esptool (from GitHub or local .bin)\n- GitHub Actions workflow for automatic PyInstaller .exe builds\n- Catppuccin Mocha dark theme via QSS + Fusion palette\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
